{
  "stem": "293.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they give a choice only to the officer, not to unlisted man, that we can go to prisoner of war to Russia or the prisoner of a war to Germany.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were officially prisoner of war of German, but they give us a choice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Many of my colleagues, because we are thinking to go to east to Romania, across Romania, go to Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Yugoslavia, take the ship to France, and-- and the Polish army was organized in-- in French in this time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was thinking different way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew the Russia never signed the Geneva Convention.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't-- I knew mentality what will happen, the Stalinist period.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That I will probably wind out someplace in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was what I was thinking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The German is signed the-- the Geneva Convention.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, they will obey the rules.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It doesn't meant they will, but this was my thinking in this time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I decide to go to German prisoner of war instead to Russian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I found out later-- and I have the book to prove it-- that the 16,000 Polish officers, and some of them the Jews were there, was killed in [NON-ENGLISH], in surrounding area.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I escape.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- the train was passing from city of Cracow, and we have to change the train to different one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when I was there, it's interesting how easy, little story can change everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we were there in the hospital-- because I have a three and a half years medical study-- the professor of anatomy from Warsaw University, Professor [NON-ENGLISH], was the officer in charge of the hospital.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That because he was a doctor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he needed an assistant, and I was his assistant.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
